235
00:13:21,410 --> 00:13:21,970
No way.

236
00:13:22,170 --> 00:13:23,090
Definitely not.

237
00:13:23,330 --> 00:13:24,770
Deng Ke has something on me.

238
00:13:25,050 --> 00:13:26,130
I can’t help you.

239
00:13:27,810 --> 00:13:30,130
