241
00:13:38,610 --> 00:13:39,170
Three.

242
00:13:41,050 --> 00:13:41,570
Two.

243
00:13:43,530 --> 00:13:44,010
One.

244
00:13:46,690 --> 00:13:47,490
Hold on please.

245
00:13:49,650 --> 00:13:50,770
Besides me,

246
00:13:51,850 --> 00:13:53,090
