247
00:14:33,090 --> 00:14:34,530
Jiang Jun, are you crazy?

248
00:14:36,810 --> 00:14:37,370
Jiang Jun?

249
00:14:39,050 --> 00:14:39,650
Jiang Jun?

250
00:14:40,890 --> 00:14:41,370
Jiang Jun.

251
